{
  "stem": "7832.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's cousin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were trying to keep her alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She died just a couple of weeks after we were there, in the very early days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her sister and I remained, and we tried to be together as much as we-- we could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't on the outside, and most of the time inside the barrack we couldn't show that we belong together, because they used to separate people that became close to one another.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They immediately put them-- took them apart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you don't have a relationship or support system, because we were being treated like we were nothings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, a bug in the mud was better off than we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every day at [INAUDIBLE] appell, we were out there in the rain and in the mud, and-- and people crying and starving and-- and being sick, being afraid to go to seek for help.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, there was no help, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And just constant, constant torture and misery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- it was just-- most of us said we would be better off dead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a lot of people did go to the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was electricity in the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Every time there was a transport coming through, the electricity went up, and the-- the-- the barbed wires were electrified.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it was-- they-- they were controlling it, when it was on and when it was off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When it was on, people would walk up to it just to die.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When they saw that too many people were taking their own lives, that didn't satisfy them too well, because they wanted them to die when they wanted them to die, and not when the people wanted them to die.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
